(SCHUMANN LAB IOS APP STORE RELEASE GUIDE \(MAC MINI\)) Tj
T*
(===================================================) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(Prepared for: moving from Windows/WSL development to macOS signing and App Store release.) Tj
T*
(Prepared on: 2026-03-02.) Tj
T*
T*
(1. What Is Already Scaffolded In This Repo) Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(- `capacitor.config.json` exists and is set to:) Tj
T*
(- `appId`: `com.patrickbitner.schumannlab`) Tj
T*
(- `appName`: `Schumann Lab`) Tj
T*
(- `webDir`: `www`) Tj
T*
(- `package.json` includes Capacitor dependencies and iOS scripts:) Tj
T*
(- `npm run cap:prepare`) Tj
T*
(- `npm run cap:add:ios`) Tj
T*
(- `npm run cap:sync:ios`) Tj
T*
(- `npm run cap:open:ios`) Tj
T*
(- `npm run cap:doctor`) Tj
T*
(- `tools/prepare_capacitor_webdir.js` builds `www/` by copying:) Tj
T*
(- `index.html`) Tj
T*
(- `styles.css`) Tj
T*
(- `app.js`) Tj
T*
(- `assets/`) Tj
T*
T*
(2. Mac Mini Prerequisites) Tj
T*
(-------------------------) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(1. Install latest Xcode from the Mac App Store.) Tj
T*
(2. Open Xcode once and accept license/install components.) Tj
T*
(3. Install Node.js LTS \(recommended: 20+\).) Tj
T*
(4. Ensure you can run:) Tj
T*
(- `node -v`) Tj
T*
(- `npm -v`) Tj
T*
(- `xcodebuild -version`) Tj
T*
(5. Sign into Xcode with the Apple ID in your Apple Developer account.) Tj
T*
(6. Verify your Apple Developer Program membership is active.) Tj
T*
T*
(3. First-Time Project Setup On Mac) Tj
T*
(----------------------------------) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(From repo root:) Tj
T*
T*
(    npm install) Tj
T*
