(    npm run cap:prepare) Tj
T*
(    npm run cap:add:ios) Tj
T*
(    npm run cap:sync:ios) Tj
T*
(    npm run cap:open:ios) Tj
T*
T*
(Notes:) Tj
T*
(- `npm run cap:add:ios` is first-time only. After that, use `cap:sync:ios`.) Tj
T*
(- If `ios/` already exists later, skip `cap:add:ios`.) Tj
T*
T*
(4. Daily Update Flow \(After You Change Web Code\)) Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(    npm run cap:sync:ios) Tj
T*
(    npm run cap:open:ios) Tj
T*
T*
(This refreshes the native iOS shell with latest web assets.) Tj
T*
T*
(5. Xcode Signing And Build Settings) Tj
T*
(-----------------------------------) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(In Xcode \(ios/App/App.xcworkspace\):) Tj
T*
T*
(1. Target: `App` -> `Signing & Capabilities`) Tj
T*
(2. Enable `Automatically manage signing`) Tj
T*
(3. Select your Team) Tj
T*
(4. Confirm Bundle ID: `com.patrickbitner.schumannlab`) Tj
T*
(5. Set version numbers:) Tj
T*
(- Marketing Version \(example: `2.6.7`\)) Tj
T*
(- Build Number \(increment each upload, example: `26701`, `26702`, ...\)) Tj
T*
(6. App icons:) Tj
T*
(- Add final icons in `Assets.xcassets`) Tj
T*
(7. If you need background audio behavior:) Tj
T*
(- Add capability `Background Modes`) Tj
T*
(- Enable `Audio, AirPlay, and Picture in Picture`) Tj
T*
(- Re-test battery behavior and lock-screen/foreground transitions) Tj
T*
T*
(6. App Store Connect Setup) Tj
T*
(--------------------------) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(In App Store Connect:) Tj
T*
T*
(1. Create new app record:) Tj
T*
(- Platform: iOS) Tj
T*
(- Name: Schumann Lab) Tj
T*
(- Primary language) Tj
T*
