(- Bundle ID: `com.patrickbitner.schumannlab`) Tj
T*
(2. Fill app metadata:) Tj
T*
(- Description, keywords, support URL, marketing URL \(if any\)) Tj
T*
(- Screenshots for required device sizes) Tj
T*
(3. Complete App Privacy questionnaire.) Tj
T*
(4. Set age rating and content rights info.) Tj
T*
(5. Add TestFlight testers \(internal first, external after\).) Tj
T*
T*
(7. Upload Build From Xcode) Tj
T*
(--------------------------) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(1. In Xcode set destination to `Any iOS Device \(arm64\)`.) Tj
T*
(2. Menu: `Product` -> `Archive`.) Tj
T*
(3. In Organizer select archive -> `Distribute App`.) Tj
T*
(4. Choose `App Store Connect`.) Tj
T*
(5. Upload and wait for processing in App Store Connect.) Tj
T*
(6. Attach the processed build to your app version, then submit for review.) Tj
T*
T*
(8. Recommended TestFlight Gate Before Submission) Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(- Audio starts and stops correctly in Explore and Meditate modes.) Tj
T*
(- Reverb space switching works \(`None`, `Forest`, `Temple`\).) Tj
T*
(- Breathing orb behavior and flash effects render smoothly on real iPhone.) Tj
T*
(- No crashes when switching tabs repeatedly.) Tj
T*
(- Session timer, journaling, and exports behave as expected.) Tj
T*
T*
(9. Important Time-Sensitive Policy Check) Tj
T*
(----------------------------------------) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(Apple requirements can change each cycle. Check current upload requirements before archiving.) Tj
T*
(As of this guide date \(2026-03-02\), Apple posted upcoming App Store submission requirements) Tj
T*
(with an April 2026 enforcement window.) Tj
T*
(Before your first submission, re-check:) Tj
T*
T*
(- https://developer.apple.com/news/?id=utw4yhtp) Tj
T*
(- https://developer.apple.com/app-store/submitting/) Tj
T*
(- https://developer.apple.com/app-store/review/guidelines/) Tj
T*
T*
(10. Quick Troubleshooting) Tj
T*
(-------------------------) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(- Signing error:) Tj
T*
(- Re-select Team, confirm Bundle ID not used by another app in your account.) Tj
T*
