(- Build uploaded but not visible:) Tj
T*
(- Wait for App Store Connect processing \(can take minutes to hours\).) Tj
T*
(- Web changes not showing in iOS app:) Tj
T*
(- Run `npm run cap:sync:ios` again, then clean build folder in Xcode.) Tj
T*
(- App Review audio/background concerns:) Tj
T*
(- Keep background audio behavior intentional and documented in review notes.) Tj
T*
T*
